8
00:00:53,152 --> 00:00:54,772
The input-output ratio is too low.

9
00:00:55,132 --> 00:00:56,711
We'll meet soon, okay?

10
00:00:59,012 --> 00:01:00,251
Once I see him,

11
00:01:00,692 --> 00:01:02,391
I'll finish this painting.

12
00:01:03,991 --> 00:01:05,012
