16
00:01:10,891 --> 00:01:11,711
Him.

17
00:01:12,632 --> 00:01:15,332
Don't touch my painting.

18
00:01:15,552 --> 00:01:16,912
It's not dry yet.

19
00:01:17,412 --> 00:01:19,332
Don't touch the pink one next to it.

20
00:01:19,912 --> 00:01:22,032
Jiayi, that's the one next to it.

21
00:01:22,032 --> 00:01:22,832
Jiayi.

22
00:01:23,052 --> 00:01:23,931
Jiayi.

23
00:01:25,371 --> 00:01:26,991
